    </FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font face="Haettenschweiler, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif" size="5" COLOR="#000000">Strategy</Font></TD><TD><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">So this deck is not very original, i know but he was quite efficient :-), except against moria troll (dammit!)<br />
<br />
The free people part is able to survive against nazgul or dunlend rush at the beginning of the game. After that, the archery power can deal with all the shadow, and if you have a problem with a big minion i m sure ara or lego can slaughter it with the help of merry :-)<br />
<br />
The shadow part tends to slow you opponent but it is able to kill him easily too. The most important card is the pale blade (lol) which can offer you the victory. As for the tip/lord combo, it&#39;s just a trick for DH fellow.<br />
<br />
In conclusion, this deck was a good choice for the PS, but i only did 37 on 90 :-( (because of bastian winkelhaus and jonas skali lol )<br />
<br />
So just have fun playing this deck :-) </FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font face="Haettenschweiler, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif" size="5" COLOR="#000000"> </Font></TD><TD><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">DeckTech <BR> For the Players, By the Players  <BR>www.decktech.net </FONT></TD></TR></table> 
